<item>
    <title>Vagrant 關機沒用到的機器</title>
    <link>https://malagege.github.io/blog/posts/Vagrant-%E9%97%9C%E6%A9%9F%E6%B2%92%E7%94%A8%E5%88%B0%E7%9A%84%E6%A9%9F%E5%99%A8/</link>
